sellerCard.oneLiner: Expert Custom PHP, HTML, CSS, JavaScript and MYSQL Developer
sellerCard.description:
Looking for a skilled and experienced PHP developer to bring your next web project to life? Look no further! I am an expert in custom PHP development, as well as Laravel and Code-igniter frameworks. 

With a deep understanding of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and MySQL, I can create a web application that is tailored to your specific needs and goals. Whether you're looking for a simple brochure website or a complex web application, I have the skills and experience to deliver a high-quality solution that meets your requirements. With my focus on user-experience, performance, and scalability.

description.content:
Hi, I am Farhan Saqib an Experienced and Professional Full Stack PHP Web Developer and write any kind of script using HTML5, CSS3, BOOTSTRAP, JAVASCRIPT, J-QUERY, PHP, and MySQL.


I can do complete Web APP Development

from SCRATCH with an admin panel according to your need in Custom PHP / Codeigniter and also use the Git and Github if required.


Note: Please Inbox me first before ordering for estimate which should be excluding the weekends.


This service includes :


Basic package :

I will fix any small bug using HTML5, CSS3, JAVASCRIPT, J-QUERY, PHP and MYSQL

This package will cover any small/tiny bug fix for your webs


Gold Package :

Everything in Basic Package

I will add a cool feature to your existing website using HTML5, CSS3, JAVASCRIPT, J-QUERY, PHP and MYSQL

New medium Feature


Premium Package :

I will create a completely new website from scratch using HTML5, CSS3, JAVASCRIPT, J-QUERY, PHP and MYSQL

PHP will use as Core PHP OR Codeigniter

Custom PHP included


Why hire me :

I am an Expert and professional in this field with 10+ years of experience

I am good communicator

Your bugs will be completely fixed

100% Satisfaction Guaranteed

questionsAndAnswers.question: What services Should i provide?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: HTML5, CSS3, Java-Script, j Query, Core PHP / Codeigniter and MYSQL.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is Basic Package Covers?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Its just a Package where i can fix a tiny bug with in your Web Application OR Script using HTML5, CSS3, Java-Script, j Query, Core PHP / Codeigniter and MYSQL.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is Gold Package Covers?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Its a Package where i can provide the service to add medium level features in your existing Web Application using HTML5, CSS3, Java-Script, j Query, Core PHP / Codeigniter and MYSQL.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is Premium Package Covers?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Its a whole Web Application including Admin Panel which can be develop from Scratch using HTML5, CSS3, Java-Script, j Query, Core PHP / Codeigniter and MYSQL.
